title: 'pretty definitive' no on more city money for arts center
text: Don’t expect Orlando to dip deeper into its pockets to pay for the next phase of the Dr. Phillips Performing Arts Center. Orlando Mayor Buddy Dyer gave a "pretty definitive" no when asked by Orange County Mayor Teresa Jacobs if he’d entertain that idea during last week’s meeting of the Tourist... ...
